Projects

Below you'll find a few of my more interesting projects with an image and a small description.

Gir 3D Model - Maya

I used Maya to create a 3D model of Gir from Invader Zim and learned how to deform and keyframe him.

Anaglyph Creator - Python

I created a book cover using Adobe Illustrator for Ray Bradbury's The Exiles for a previously taken art class.
